Re: Ballad of Silicon Slim - v13 i10
</A>
</H3>
<address>
Laurence R. Brothers
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:quasar@puddle.bellcore.com ">
quasar@puddle.bellcore.com 
</A>&gt;
</address>
<i>
Tue, 4 Feb 92 15:28:38 -0500
