<H3><A NAME="subj6.1">
Risks of Automated Phone Operators (RE: <A HREF="/Risks/13.24.html">RISKS-13.24</A>)
</A>
</H3>
<address>
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:olson@husc.harvard.edu">
olson@husc.harvard.edu
</A>&gt;
